# Report Permissions Contract

Always preserve this behavior:

- Author can edit own report.
- Superuser can edit any report.
- Non-owner and non-superuser cannot edit чужой report.

When changing `updateReport`/access checks:

- Validate owner lookup and reportOwnerId usage across rebuild flow.
- Ensure date conflict checks are performed in owner scope.
- Ensure old lessons/transactions cleanup uses report owner context.
- Re-run `npm run smoke:reports:permissions`.
